      "title": "On the limit measure to stochastic Volterra equations",
      "abstract": "The paper is concerned with a limit measure of stochastic Volterra equation driven by a spatially homogeneous Wiener process with values in the space of real tempered distributions. Necessary and sufficient conditions for the existence of the limit measure are provided and a form of any limit measure is given as well."
